# But: ship a starter dataset so Streamlit Cloud renders on first load.
# These are forecasts/snapshots; safe to refresh weekly. Daily-volatile files
# (vegas_lines, injury_report, upcoming_game_predictions) stay excluded.
!data/champion_probabilities.csv
!data/round_advancement.csv
!data/historical_playoff_features.csv
!data/backtest_results.csv
!data/backtest_round_brier.csv
!data/backtest_calibration.csv
!data/nba_playoffs_games_*.csv
!data/nba_playoffs_boxscores_*.csv

# Ship the trained model so the cloud Predict button works on first click.
!model.pkl

